( agence france - presse , london , 1 st ) - the spokesman of the mars exploration program , bart , said that a u . s . satellite is unable to link up with the landing boat of the european little hunting dog no . 2 , which has already landed on mars , and the hope to collect signals from the little dog no . 2 is now in the hope of its mother ship , the mars express .
balaguer said , " we have not obtained any further results . "
he said , " now we have placed our hope on its mother ship mars express , waiting for it to collect intelligence . "
the us odyssey spacecraft on mars failed to receive any information on the 2 nd from the european mars detector dog , and the little dog ii still continued to search for signs of life on mars after it landed on mars .
the mars odyssey spacecraft is another exploration mission launched by the us space agency into mars .
the european space agency in paris said that the man - made satellite made by the european - made mars express has been launched to the extreme orbit of mars , hoping that it will still send back some signals next week .
the dog no. 2 was originally scheduled to land on mars during the christmas , but its signal is still hard to find .
on december 2 nd , after leaving the mother ship mars express , the little dog became the first european spacecraft to land on another star .
during the 18 - day flight mission , the little dog no . 2 plans to test the rock , soil , signal transmission mode , or all life on mars .
scientists have boldly predicted that the british spacecraft may be bogged down in a pit .
pakistani president musharraf wins confidence vote in senate and house of representatives
( agence france - presse , islamabad , january 1 ) - pakistani president musharraf today won the confidence vote in the house of representatives and the house of representatives under the circumstances of the islamic fundamentalists ' abstention and opposition resistance . this confidence vote has determined that musharraf 's rule will continue until 2007 .
" musharraf has won a majority vote in the parliament , " information minister rashid told afp .
no members of the parliament voted against him . "
in the 342 - seat house of representatives , 191 members of the house of representatives voted in support of musharraf , islamic fundamentalists abstention , and opposition parties resisted the controversial confidence vote .
musharraf made concessions to the six muslim political parties , agreeing to resign from the post of army commander - in - chief , and at the same time seeking the approval of the supreme court within one month after the dissolution of the parliament .
in the 100 - seat senate , 56 senators voted in support of musharraf , 42 muslim fundamentalists and opposition members abstention or resisted .
musharraf won the political power in the october 1999 coup and subsequently refused to step down .
