china seizes 186 tons of us beef
( agence france - presse , beijing , 2 nd ) - china 's state - owned media , " beijing youth daily , " reported today that due to market fears that the import of beef is infected with mad cow disease , relevant authorities carried out market inspection and detained 186 tons of u . s . beef in beijing yesterday .
according to the ministry of agriculture 's proposal , the beef will be destroyed after testing , the beijing youth daily said .
more than 30 countries in the world suspended imports of us beef last week , and china is also one of them .
except for milk and other milk products , leather and photo - taking , all cattle - related products are listed in the ban .
the beijing agricultural bureau has recently issued a series of preventive and control and supervision laws and launched a comprehensive market inspection , the beijing youth daily reported .
at present , there is no case of mad cow disease in china .
this is the second time in the past week that the authorities have detained 60 kilograms of beef from the us state of washington , where mad cow cases have been reported in a us cargo ship in ningbo , zhejiang province .
although statistics from the ministry of commerce show that china imported meat worth 532 million us dollars from the united states last year , the import of us beef is still unknown .
from january to july last year , china imported a total of $ 316 million worth of meat from the united states .
