( agence france - presse , tokyo , 5 th ) - japanese prime minister junichiro koizumi vowed at a press conference on the first working day after the new year holidays that he would continue to promote economic reform this year . he said : " although the economic situation is still in difficulty , we can finally see signs of recovery . "
