koizumi has promised to completely privatization the postal service with 28,000 employees in 2007 .
japan 's postal service industry is regarded as the world 's largest bank by relying on its 355 - trillion - yen ( us $ 3.3 - trillion ) savings and insurance fund .
however , this large - scale plan still faces strong opposition from conservative congressmen .
the plan started in 1993 when koizumi was minister of postal service .
