from the handling of a full - scale parliamentary election in 1991 , the handling of the presidential election in 1994 , the freeze of the provincial government organizations in 1997 , and the establishment of the national assembly in 2000 , this series of twists and turns in the process of revising the constitution are in fact the track of the taiwan people 's strengthening of sovereignty and the legitimacy of democracy .
