over the past 30 years , the consumer council 's contribution to the protection of consumer interests is obvious to all .
to assess the effectiveness of the consumer council , it is best not to see if there is any substantive improvement in consumer interests .
i agree with president chen just now that after 30 years , not only consumers have a clear understanding of their own interests , but also all sectors of the community have attached importance to the rights and interests of consumers , which is the result of the efforts of the consumer council and the government .
the consumer council regularly conducts testing of products , conducts market surveys and studies on different products and services , and releases fair and objective market information to the public through the " choice " monthly .
the " choice " monthly is deeply trusted by the public , and the development of the internet version of the " choice " monthly will give more effective play to its functions and help consumers obtain market information in a more convenient way .
the consumer council has 11 district consumer advisory centres and 16 telephone hotlines to provide information on goods and services to consumers and to receive complaints from consumers .
since its establishment , the number of enquiries received by the consumer council has increased from several thousand in the 1970 s to 146,000 last year , an increase of more than 20 times , indicating that more and more consumers will make reference to the consumer council 's report and advice before selecting products and services .
in addition , the consumer council has handled more than 26,000 complaints this year .
