at present , the legislative authorities in hong kong are discussing various improvement proposals to tighten the existing legislation against terrorist financing and to actively coordinate with international standards and situations , such as the new recommendations of the financial action task force on money laundering .
in addition , we are seeking to introduce more comprehensive disclosure legislation to facilitate the reporting of suspicious transactions by the relevant organisations and individuals .
