we have carried out arduous and arduous struggle against the sudden sars epidemic , achieved a major victory in this stage , our country 's economy has maintained a good momentum of development , our per capita gdp has exceeded $ 1,000 , and the " shenzhou - 5 " manned space flight has been successful , the chinese nation 's dream of flying in the sky has become a reality , the people 's unity , social progress , and the people 's living standards have further improved .
china 's achievements in all fields have attracted worldwide attention , and the people of the whole country have made tremendous efforts in this regard , showing their courage and strength to defy hardships and difficulties and create miracles .
looking forward to the new year , we are full of confidence and hope .
taking a general view of the domestic and international situation , our country is at an important strategic opportunity period that must be firmly grasped and can be accomplished .
