last year , the beijing organizing committee for the olympic games also specially designed a classroom program with the beijing olympic logo for young students .
the concept of " green olympics " is to use the idea of sustainable development , such as environmental protection and ecological balance , to prepare and host the olympic games .
we hope that these textbooks will be able to standardize the behavior of young students as stipulated in the class , so that they will gradually become the practitioners and propaganda agents of the " green olympics " concept .
education is one of the core contents of the olympic movement , and is also an important embodiment of the " olympics of humanity . "
the real purpose of the olympic movement is to educate young people from a new angle and in a new way , to promote the harmonious development of young people , and to make contributions to the establishment of a peaceful and beautiful world .
therefore , the integration of sports and education has not only opened up a new vista for the development of education , but also made the olympic games more educational .
the " green olympics " is one of the three major concepts for beijing to host the 2008 olympic games .
the core content is to greatly improve the quality of the capital 's environment , create a beautiful environment for the olympic games , and build an ecological city .
to this end , it is necessary to extensively adopt environmental protection technology and means , promote environmental control , urban and rural greening and beautification , and the development of the environmental protection industry on a large scale and in a variety of ways , continuously enhance the awareness of environmental protection in the whole society , and encourage the public to actively participate in various activities to improve the ecological environment .
