the security council has successively adopted four resolutions , namely , 1271 ( 1999 ) , 1314 ( 2000 ) , 1379 ( 2001 ) , and 1,460 ( 2003 ) , providing an important framework for the work of protecting children .
the un peacekeeping operations in some regions have taken the protection of children as an important task , including the appointment of children 's protection advisers , and in the process of helping the country to carry out the program of disarming , rejoining , and returning to society , the special needs of children have been fully taken into consideration .
some peace agreements promoted or participated in by the united nations also include provisions on the protection of children .
