on the same day , hundreds of thousands of tourists gathered in the streets of los angeles to watch the 115 th " roses " parade , and to experience the festive atmosphere brought about by the new year amid the brilliant performance of the band and the magnificent and colorful float parade .
to prevent terrorist activities , the los angeles police have adopted unprecedented tight security measures .
more than 1,000 policemen and a large number of plain - clothes mixed into the crowd to monitor suspicious figures .
the police also used various measures , such as video cameras , helicopters , and police dogs , to monitor the scene of the march and to conduct strict checks on suspicious items .
on that day , about 100 vehicles parked near the procession line were searched by the police .
