it has been learned that since there are a large number of cross - boundary vehicles at the shenzhen port , such as the average number of cross - boundary vehicles at huanggang control point on a daily basis , and the number of man kam to control point is as high as 25,000 , it is quite difficult to ensure the smooth flow of the port and to carry out health quarantine for all drivers .
in order to do a good job in the work of checking the temperature of the entry - exit drivers and the inspection and quarantine system , the shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has overcome all kinds of difficulties . in addition to increasing the number of personnel from the inside to the front line of the port , it has recently urgently recruited more than 250,000 people . after conducting concentrated training , all of them have been strengthened to the front line of the port to ensure the safety and smooth progress of the port . at the same time ,
the shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has requested all relevant units and exit - entry drivers to pay attention to the fact that the " entry - exit health quarantine declaration card " can be obtained at the work points of the " entry - exit vehicle and cargo ( personnel ) inspection and quarantine supervision book " or the work points of the inspection and quarantine inspection card .
